Class HemfMisc.EmfSetMiterLimit

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.hemf.record.emf.HemfMisc.EmfSetMiterLimit

    public static class HemfMisc.EmfSetMiterLimit
extends java.lang.Object
implements HemfRecord
    The EMR_SETMITERLIMIT record specifies the limit for the length of miter joins for the playback device context.(EMR_SETMITERLIMIT记录指定播放设备上下文的斜接长度限制。)
